listitem.para:
Harmonize syntax for function types as 
int->int and (String, int)->boolean.
Introduce automatic constructors that initialize the fields, using
optional named parameters. 
This means that it is not necessary to write the code for the constructor,
nor for a simple creation function. Example:

class LinkedList<T>
{
  T head;
  ?LinkedList<T> tail;
}
...
LinkedList<int> l = 
  new LinkedList(head: 1, 
                 tail: new LinkedList(head: 2, tail: null));
